<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It"&gt;18It Itivuttakapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/2"&gt;2 Dukanipāta&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/18It/2/2.1"&gt;2.1 Paṭhamavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;2.1.5 Paṭhamasīlasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Dukanipāta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Paṭhamavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Paṭhamasīlasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_198"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;32.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;198&lt;/span&gt;Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_199"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;199&lt;/span&gt;“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye. Katamehi dvīhi? Pāpakena ca sīlena, pāpikāya ca diṭṭhiyā. Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato puggalo yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye”ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati—  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_200"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;200&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;“Pāpakena ca sīlena,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;pāpikāya ca diṭṭhiyā;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Etehi dvīhi dhammehi,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;yo samannāgato naro;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kāyassa bhedā duppañño,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;nirayaṃ sopapajjatī”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_18It_201"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;201&lt;/span&gt;Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_18It_202"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;202&lt;/span&gt;Pañcamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="268406" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 2.1.4 Atapanīyasutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="266885" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="268408" title="Go to next page"&gt;2.1.6 Dutiyasīlasutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
